===Etymology===
Greek ''rhegos'' blanket, ''lithos'' stone)

===Noun===
'''regolith'''

#{{geology}} The layer of loose [[rock]], resting on the [[bedrock]], that constitutes the surface of most land (and the surface of the [[moon]] etc.).

